text: The manager some 18 yr old kid, trying to do everything by himself. Made my pizza wrong, argued with me about it, and took forever to really make it. Saw him using his hands to place it in the box. I ordered pan, though the crust was thin and crispy. Never coming back!

text: Horrible. Don't order from here. I customized my pizza and it came out very cold and I told them to make it fresh and it was stale. When I called to give feedback the guy on the phone was rude and disrespectful. Very shocked.

name: Ashish Mishra
text: This place is running in a parallel universe. Check the expiry date on the parmesan packets... Although I am a big Pizza hut fan... this was a total thumbs down.pics taken on 12th Jan 2017

text: We didn't even order. We walked in, and we were completely ignored. We said hello, but the cashier continued to talk to his coworker. We waited for a few minutes, then left. Go to the one on Lee highway. Never going back.
